annotationA: 60S ribosomal protein L19; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: centrosome duplication; mitotic spindle elongation; translation; Belongs to the eukaryotic ribosomal protein eL19 family
annotationB: 40S ribosomal protein S2; Has a specific developmental role during oogenesis and a general role in protein synthesis as a component of the small ribosomal subunit
